## Project Structure

```
neurocredit/
│
├── ml/                          # Machine Learning layer
│   ├── train.py                 # Data generation + model training
│   ├── score.py                 # Inference engine (used by backend)
│   ├── training_data.csv        # 5,000 synthetic profiles
│   └── artifacts/
│       ├── model.joblib         # Trained GBR model
│       ├── scaler.joblib        # StandardScaler (fitted)
│       ├── features.json        # Feature names in order
│       └── feature_importance.json
│
├── contracts/
│   └── NeuroCredit.sol          # ERC-5484 Soul Bound Token contract
│
├── backend/
│   └── main.py                  # FastAPI server (2 endpoints)
│
├── frontend/
│   └── index.html               # Complete 4-page app (zero dependencies)
│
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
```

