## Why Not Just Use CIBIL?

| | CIBIL | Finbox / CreditVidya | NeuroCredit |
|---|---|---|---|
| Scores gig workers | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Alternative data | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ |
| User owns their score | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Score is on-chain | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Non-transferable / unfakeable | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Works with DeFi protocols | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Zero personal data to lenders | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Lender trusts blockchain, not company | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |

